{"id":"entertainment_beginner_001","q":{"en":"Which Japanese animation studio created 'Spirited Away'?","zh":"哪家日本动画工作室制作了《千与千寻》？","ja":"『千と千尋の神隠し』を制作した日本のアニメスタジオはどこですか？","es":"¿Qué estudio de animación japonés creó 'El viaje de Chihiro'?"},"c":[{"en":"Toei Animation","zh":"东映动画","ja":"東映アニメーション","es":"Toei Animation"},{"en":"Studio Ghibli","zh":"吉卜力工作室","ja":"スタジオジブリ","es":"Studio Ghibli"},{"en":"Sunrise","zh":"日升动画","ja":"サンライズ","es":"Sunrise"},{"en":"Madhouse","zh":"疯人院动画","ja":"マッドハウス","es":"Madhouse"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Studio Ghibli was co-founded by Hayao Miyazaki and Isao Takahata in 1985 and has produced many beloved animated films.","zh":"吉卜力工作室由宫崎骏和高畑勋于1985年共同创立，制作了许多深受喜爱的动画电影。","ja":"スタジオジブリは1985年に宮崎駿と高畑勲によって共同設立され、多くの名作アニメ映画を生み出しました。","es":"Studio Ghibli fue cofundado por Hayao Miyazaki e Isao Takahata en 1985 y ha producido muchas películas animadas muy queridas."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_002","q":{"en":"What is the name of the giant monster that first appeared in a 1954 Japanese film?","zh":"1954年首次出现在日本电影中的巨型怪兽叫什么名字？","ja":"1954年の日本映画に初めて登場した巨大怪獣の名前は何ですか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama el monstruo gigante que apareció por primera vez en una película japonesa de 1954?"},"c":[{"en":"Mothra","zh":"摩斯拉","ja":"モスラ","es":"Mothra"},{"en":"Rodan","zh":"拉顿","ja":"ラドン","es":"Rodan"},{"en":"Gamera","zh":"卡美拉","ja":"ガメラ","es":"Gamera"},{"en":"Godzilla","zh":"哥斯拉","ja":"ゴジラ","es":"Godzilla"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Godzilla (Gojira) was created as a metaphor for nuclear weapons, reflecting Japan's experience with atomic bombings.","zh":"哥斯拉是作为核武器的隐喻而创造的，反映了日本遭受原子弹轰炸的经历。","ja":"ゴジラは核兵器の比喩として作られ、日本の原爆体験を反映しています。","es":"Godzilla (Gojira) fue creado como una metáfora de las armas nucleares, reflejando la experiencia de Japón con los bombardeos atómicos."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_003","q":{"en":"Who directed 'Spirited Away' and 'My Neighbor Totoro'?","zh":"谁导演了《千与千寻》和《龙猫》？","ja":"『千と千尋の神隠し』と『となりのトトロ』の監督は誰ですか？","es":"¿Quién dirigió 'El viaje de Chihiro' y 'Mi vecino Totoro'?"},"c":[{"en":"Isao Takahata","zh":"高畑勋","ja":"高畑勲","es":"Isao Takahata"},{"en":"Mamoru Hosoda","zh":"细田守","ja":"細田守","es":"Mamoru Hosoda"},{"en":"Hayao Miyazaki","zh":"宫崎骏","ja":"宮崎駿","es":"Hayao Miyazaki"},{"en":"Makoto Shinkai","zh":"新海诚","ja":"新海誠","es":"Makoto Shinkai"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Hayao Miyazaki is often called the 'Walt Disney of Japan' and won an Academy Award for Spirited Away in 2003.","zh":"宫崎骏常被称为'日本的华特·迪士尼'，2003年凭《千与千寻》获得奥斯卡奖。","ja":"宮崎駿は『日本のウォルト・ディズニー』と呼ばれ、2003年に『千と千尋の神隠し』でアカデミー賞を受賞しました。","es":"Hayao Miyazaki es a menudo llamado el 'Walt Disney de Japón' y ganó un Oscar por El viaje de Chihiro en 2003."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_004","q":{"en":"What is the traditional Japanese two-person comedy style called?","zh":"日本传统的双人喜剧形式叫什么？","ja":"日本の伝統的な二人組のお笑いスタイルを何と言いますか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama el estilo tradicional japonés de comedia de dos personas?"},"c":[{"en":"Rakugo","zh":"落语","ja":"落語","es":"Rakugo"},{"en":"Manzai","zh":"漫才","ja":"漫才","es":"Manzai"},{"en":"Kabuki","zh":"歌舞伎","ja":"歌舞伎","es":"Kabuki"},{"en":"Kyogen","zh":"狂言","ja":"狂言","es":"Kyogen"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Manzai features a funny man (boke) and a straight man (tsukkomi) performing rapid-fire comedy dialogues.","zh":"漫才由装傻角色（ボケ）和吐槽角色（ツッコミ）表演快节奏的喜剧对话。","ja":"漫才はボケとツッコミの二人がテンポよく掛け合いをする笑いのスタイルです。","es":"El manzai presenta a un cómico (boke) y un hombre serio (tsukkomi) realizando diálogos cómicos rápidos."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_005","q":{"en":"Which Japanese film won the Academy Award for Best Animated Feature in 2003?","zh":"哪部日本电影在2003年获得了奥斯卡最佳动画长片奖？","ja":"2003年にアカデミー長編アニメ映画賞を受賞した日本映画はどれですか？","es":"¿Qué película japonesa ganó el Oscar a la Mejor Película Animada en 2003?"},"c":[{"en":"Princess Mononoke","zh":"幽灵公主","ja":"もののけ姫","es":"La princesa Mononoke"},{"en":"My Neighbor Totoro","zh":"龙猫","ja":"となりのトトロ","es":"Mi vecino Totoro"},{"en":"Howl's Moving Castle","zh":"哈尔的移动城堡","ja":"ハウルの動く城","es":"El castillo ambulante"},{"en":"Spirited Away","zh":"千与千寻","ja":"千と千尋の神隠し","es":"El viaje de Chihiro"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Spirited Away was the first non-English language film to win the Academy Award for Best Animated Feature.","zh":"《千与千寻》是第一部获得奥斯卡最佳动画长片奖的非英语电影。","ja":"『千と千尋の神隠し』は非英語映画として初めてアカデミー長編アニメ映画賞を受賞しました。","es":"El viaje de Chihiro fue la primera película en idioma no inglés en ganar el Oscar a la Mejor Película Animada."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_006","q":{"en":"What is the most-watched annual music show on Japanese TV, broadcast on New Year's Eve?","zh":"日本电视上每年除夕夜播出的收视率最高的音乐节目是什么？","ja":"大晦日に放送される日本で最も視聴される年末音楽番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Cuál es el programa musical anual más visto en la TV japonesa, transmitido en Nochevieja?"},"c":[{"en":"Music Station","zh":"音乐站","ja":"ミュージックステーション","es":"Music Station"},{"en":"Kohaku Uta Gassen","zh":"红白歌合战","ja":"紅白歌合戦","es":"Kohaku Uta Gassen"},{"en":"Best Hit Kayousai","zh":"Best Hit歌谣祭","ja":"ベストヒット歌謡祭","es":"Best Hit Kayousai"},{"en":"FNS Music Festival","zh":"FNS音乐节","ja":"FNS歌謡祭","es":"FNS Music Festival"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Kohaku Uta Gassen has been broadcast by NHK since 1951 and divides performers into Red (women) and White (men) teams.","zh":"红白歌合战自1951年起由NHK播出，将歌手分为红组（女性）和白组（男性）。","ja":"紅白歌合戦は1951年からNHKで放送され、出場歌手を紅組（女性）と白組（男性）に分けて競います。","es":"Kohaku Uta Gassen se transmite por NHK desde 1951 y divide a los artistas en equipos Rojo (mujeres) y Blanco (hombres)."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_007","q":{"en":"What is the name of Japan's largest public broadcasting organization?","zh":"日本最大的公共广播组织叫什么？","ja":"日本最大の公共放送局の名前は何ですか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama la organización de radiodifusión pública más grande de Japón?"},"c":[{"en":"NHK","zh":"NHK","ja":"NHK","es":"NHK"},{"en":"Fuji TV","zh":"富士电视台","ja":"フジテレビ","es":"Fuji TV"},{"en":"TV Asahi","zh":"朝日电视台","ja":"テレビ朝日","es":"TV Asahi"},{"en":"TBS","zh":"TBS电视台","ja":"TBS","es":"TBS"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"NHK stands for Nippon Hoso Kyokai (Japan Broadcasting Corporation) and is funded primarily by viewer fees.","zh":"NHK是日本放送协会的缩写，主要由观众缴纳的收视费支持运营。","ja":"NHKは日本放送協会の略称で、主に受信料によって運営されています。","es":"NHK significa Nippon Hoso Kyokai (Corporación de Radiodifusión de Japón) y se financia principalmente con las cuotas de los espectadores."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_008","q":{"en":"Which long-running Japanese drama series airs every morning on NHK?","zh":"NHK每天早上播出的长寿日剧系列叫什么？","ja":"NHKで毎朝放送されている長寿ドラマシリーズは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué serie de drama japonés de larga duración se emite cada mañana en NHK?"},"c":[{"en":"Taiga Drama","zh":"大河剧","ja":"大河ドラマ","es":"Taiga Drama"},{"en":"Asadora","zh":"晨间剧","ja":"朝ドラ","es":"Asadora"},{"en":"Getsu-9","zh":"月九剧","ja":"月9","es":"Getsu-9"},{"en":"Nichiyou Gekijou","zh":"日曜剧场","ja":"日曜劇場","es":"Nichiyou Gekijou"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Asadora (morning drama) has been running since 1961. Each series lasts about six months and often features a female protagonist.","zh":"晨间剧自1961年开始播出，每部约半年，通常以女性为主角。","ja":"朝ドラは1961年から続いており、各作品は約半年間放送され、女性が主人公のことが多いです。","es":"Asadora (drama matutino) se transmite desde 1961. Cada serie dura unos seis meses y suele tener una protagonista femenina."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_009","q":{"en":"Which famous Japanese director made 'Seven Samurai' and 'Rashomon'?","zh":"哪位著名日本导演制作了《七武士》和《罗生门》？","ja":"『七人の侍』と『羅生門』を監督した有名な日本の映画監督は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué famoso director japonés hizo 'Los siete samuráis' y 'Rashomon'?"},"c":[{"en":"Yasujiro Ozu","zh":"小津安二郎","ja":"小津安二郎","es":"Yasujiro Ozu"},{"en":"Akira Kurosawa","zh":"黑泽明","ja":"黒澤明","es":"Akira Kurosawa"},{"en":"Kenji Mizoguchi","zh":"沟口健二","ja":"溝口健二","es":"Kenji Mizoguchi"},{"en":"Takeshi Kitano","zh":"北野武","ja":"北野武","es":"Takeshi Kitano"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Akira Kurosawa is considered one of the most influential filmmakers in cinema history and inspired directors like George Lucas and Steven Spielberg.","zh":"黑泽明被认为是电影史上最有影响力的导演之一，启发了乔治·卢卡斯和斯蒂芬·斯皮尔伯格等导演。","ja":"黒澤明は映画史上最も影響力のある映画監督の一人とされ、ジョージ・ルーカスやスティーブン・スピルバーグに影響を与えました。","es":"Akira Kurosawa es considerado uno de los cineastas más influyentes de la historia e inspiró a directores como George Lucas y Steven Spielberg."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_010","q":{"en":"What is the Japanese comedy term for the 'funny man' role in a manzai duo?","zh":"漫才组合中'搞笑担当'的日语术语是什么？","ja":"漫才コンビでボケを担当する人を何と言いますか？","es":"¿Cuál es el término japonés para el papel del 'hombre gracioso' en un dúo de manzai?"},"c":[{"en":"Tsukkomi","zh":"吐槽役","ja":"ツッコミ","es":"Tsukkomi"},{"en":"Sensei","zh":"老师","ja":"先生","es":"Sensei"},{"en":"Boke","zh":"装傻役","ja":"ボケ","es":"Boke"},{"en":"Senpai","zh":"前辈","ja":"先輩","es":"Senpai"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"The boke says absurd or silly things while the tsukkomi corrects them, often with a slap or sharp retort.","zh":"装傻役说出荒唐可笑的话，吐槽役则纠正他们，通常伴随着拍打或尖锐的反驳。","ja":"ボケがおかしなことを言い、ツッコミがツッコミを入れるのが漫才の基本スタイルです。","es":"El boke dice cosas absurdas mientras el tsukkomi lo corrige, a menudo con un golpe o una réplica aguda."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_011","q":{"en":"Which anime film by Makoto Shinkai became a massive worldwide hit in 2016?","zh":"新海诚的哪部动画电影在2016年成为全球大热门？","ja":"新海誠監督の2016年の大ヒットアニメ映画は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué película anime de Makoto Shinkai se convirtió en un gran éxito mundial en 2016?"},"c":[{"en":"Your Name","zh":"你的名字","ja":"君の名は。","es":"Your Name"},{"en":"Weathering with You","zh":"天气之子","ja":"天気の子","es":"El tiempo contigo"},{"en":"5 Centimeters Per Second","zh":"秒速五厘米","ja":"秒速5センチメートル","es":"5 centímetros por segundo"},{"en":"The Garden of Words","zh":"言叶之庭","ja":"言の葉の庭","es":"El jardín de las palabras"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"Your Name (Kimi no Na wa) earned over $380 million worldwide, making it one of the highest-grossing anime films ever.","zh":"《你的名字》全球票房超过3.8亿美元，成为有史以来票房最高的动画电影之一。","ja":"『君の名は。』は全世界で3億8000万ドル以上の興行収入を記録し、歴代アニメ映画の中でもトップクラスの成績を収めました。","es":"Your Name recaudó más de 380 millones de dólares en todo el mundo, convirtiéndola en una de las películas anime más taquilleras de la historia."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_012","q":{"en":"What is the name of Japan's major film award, often called the 'Japanese Academy Awards'?","zh":"日本的主要电影奖项，常被称为'日本奥斯卡'的是什么？","ja":"日本のアカデミー賞と呼ばれる映画賞は何ですか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama el principal premio cinematográfico de Japón, a menudo llamado los 'Premios de la Academia Japonesa'?"},"c":[{"en":"Golden Globe Japan","zh":"日本金球奖","ja":"日本ゴールデングローブ","es":"Golden Globe Japan"},{"en":"Japan Academy Film Prize","zh":"日本电影学院奖","ja":"日本アカデミー賞","es":"Premio de la Academia de Cine de Japón"},{"en":"Kinema Junpo Awards","zh":"电影旬报奖","ja":"キネマ旬報ベスト・テン","es":"Premios Kinema Junpo"},{"en":"Tokyo Film Prize","zh":"东京电影奖","ja":"東京映画賞","es":"Premio de Cine de Tokio"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"The Japan Academy Film Prize has been awarded annually since 1978 and covers categories similar to the American Academy Awards.","zh":"日本电影学院奖自1978年起每年颁发，涵盖与美国奥斯卡类似的奖项类别。","ja":"日本アカデミー賞は1978年から毎年授与されており、アメリカのアカデミー賞と同様の部門があります。","es":"El Premio de la Academia de Cine de Japón se otorga anualmente desde 1978 y cubre categorías similares a los premios de la Academia Americana."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_013","q":{"en":"Which Japanese celebrity is known as 'Beat Takeshi' and is also a famous film director?","zh":"哪位日本名人被称为'北野武'，同时也是著名电影导演？","ja":"『ビートたけし』として知られ、映画監督としても有名な日本の芸能人は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué celebridad japonesa es conocida como 'Beat Takeshi' y también es un famoso director de cine?"},"c":[{"en":"Takeshi Kitano","zh":"北野武","ja":"北野武","es":"Takeshi Kitano"},{"en":"Ken Watanabe","zh":"渡边谦","ja":"渡辺謙","es":"Ken Watanabe"},{"en":"Tadanobu Asano","zh":"浅野忠信","ja":"浅野忠信","es":"Tadanobu Asano"},{"en":"Hiroyuki Sanada","zh":"真田广之","ja":"真田広之","es":"Hiroyuki Sanada"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"Takeshi Kitano started as a comedian in the manzai duo 'Two Beat' before becoming an acclaimed international film director.","zh":"北野武最初是漫才组合'Two Beat'的搞笑艺人，后来成为国际知名电影导演。","ja":"北野武は漫才コンビ『ツービート』でお笑い芸人として活動した後、国際的に評価される映画監督になりました。","es":"Takeshi Kitano comenzó como comediante en el dúo de manzai 'Two Beat' antes de convertirse en un aclamado director de cine internacional."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_014","q":{"en":"What is the famous Japanese TV drama time slot on Fuji TV, Monday at 9 PM?","zh":"富士电视台每周一晚上9点的著名日剧时段叫什么？","ja":"フジテレビの月曜夜9時の有名なドラマ枠は何と呼ばれていますか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama la famosa franja horaria de dramas japoneses en Fuji TV, los lunes a las 9 PM?"},"c":[{"en":"Kin-8","zh":"金八","ja":"金8","es":"Kin-8"},{"en":"Getsu-9","zh":"月九","ja":"月9","es":"Getsu-9"},{"en":"Sui-10","zh":"水十","ja":"水10","es":"Sui-10"},{"en":"Nichi-9","zh":"日九","ja":"日9","es":"Nichi-9"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Getsu-9 (Monday 9) dramas were hugely popular in the 1990s and launched the careers of many famous actors.","zh":"月九剧在1990年代非常受欢迎，捧红了许多著名演员。","ja":"月9ドラマは1990年代に大人気となり、多くの有名俳優を輩出しました。","es":"Los dramas Getsu-9 (Lunes 9) fueron enormemente populares en la década de 1990 y lanzaron las carreras de muchos actores famosos."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_015","q":{"en":"Which Studio Ghibli film features a forest spirit shaped like a round, friendly creature?","zh":"哪部吉卜力电影中有一个圆胖友善的森林精灵？","ja":"丸くて親しみやすい森の精霊が登場するスタジオジブリの映画はどれですか？","es":"¿Qué película de Studio Ghibli presenta un espíritu del bosque con forma de criatura redonda y amigable?"},"c":[{"en":"Ponyo","zh":"悬崖上的金鱼姬","ja":"崖の上のポニョ","es":"Ponyo"},{"en":"My Neighbor Totoro","zh":"龙猫","ja":"となりのトトロ","es":"Mi vecino Totoro"},{"en":"Kiki's Delivery Service","zh":"魔女宅急便","ja":"魔女の宅急便","es":"Kiki: Entregas a domicilio"},{"en":"Castle in the Sky","zh":"天空之城","ja":"天空の城ラピュタ","es":"El castillo en el cielo"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Totoro has become the official mascot of Studio Ghibli and is one of the most recognizable characters in Japanese animation.","zh":"龙猫已成为吉卜力工作室的官方吉祥物，是日本动画中最具辨识度的角色之一。","ja":"トトロはスタジオジブリの公式マスコットとなり、日本アニメで最も知られるキャラクターの一つです。","es":"Totoro se ha convertido en la mascota oficial de Studio Ghibli y es uno de los personajes más reconocibles de la animación japonesa."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_016","q":{"en":"What type of Japanese entertainment involves a solo performer telling humorous stories while sitting on a cushion?","zh":"哪种日本表演艺术是由一个人坐在坐垫上讲幽默故事？","ja":"座布団の上に座って一人で面白い話をする日本の芸能は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué tipo de entretenimiento japonés involucra a un solo artista contando historias humorísticas sentado en un cojín?"},"c":[{"en":"Manzai","zh":"漫才","ja":"漫才","es":"Manzai"},{"en":"Noh","zh":"能乐","ja":"能","es":"Noh"},{"en":"Rakugo","zh":"落语","ja":"落語","es":"Rakugo"},{"en":"Bunraku","zh":"文乐","ja":"文楽","es":"Bunraku"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Rakugo performers use only a fan and a small cloth as props, relying entirely on their voice and gestures to portray multiple characters.","zh":"落语表演者只用扇子和小手帕作为道具，完全依靠声音和手势来扮演多个角色。","ja":"落語家は扇子と手ぬぐいだけを使い、声と仕草だけで複数の登場人物を演じ分けます。","es":"Los artistas de rakugo usan solo un abanico y un pequeño pañuelo como utilería, dependiendo completamente de su voz y gestos para interpretar múltiples personajes."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_017","q":{"en":"What is the annual M-1 Grand Prix in Japan?","zh":"日本的M-1大赛是什么？","ja":"日本のM-1グランプリとは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué es el M-1 Grand Prix anual en Japón?"},"c":[{"en":"A car racing competition","zh":"赛车比赛","ja":"カーレース大会","es":"Una competición de carreras de coches"},{"en":"A manzai comedy competition","zh":"漫才喜剧比赛","ja":"漫才コンテスト","es":"Una competición de comedia manzai"},{"en":"A cooking contest","zh":"烹饪比赛","ja":"料理コンテスト","es":"Un concurso de cocina"},{"en":"A singing contest","zh":"歌唱比赛","ja":"歌唱コンテスト","es":"Un concurso de canto"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"The M-1 Grand Prix has been held since 2001 and is one of the most prestigious comedy competitions in Japan, featuring manzai duos.","zh":"M-1大赛自2001年开始举办，是日本最负盛名的喜剧比赛之一，以漫才组合为主。","ja":"M-1グランプリは2001年から開催されており、漫才コンビが出場する日本で最も権威あるお笑いコンテストの一つです。","es":"El M-1 Grand Prix se celebra desde 2001 y es una de las competiciones de comedia más prestigiosas de Japón, con dúos de manzai."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_018","q":{"en":"Which Japanese actor starred in 'The Last Samurai' alongside Tom Cruise?","zh":"哪位日本演员与汤姆·克鲁斯一起主演了《最后的武士》？","ja":"トム・クルーズと共に『ラストサムライ』に出演した日本の俳優は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué actor japonés protagonizó 'El último samurái' junto a Tom Cruise?"},"c":[{"en":"Tadanobu Asano","zh":"浅野忠信","ja":"浅野忠信","es":"Tadanobu Asano"},{"en":"Koji Yakusho","zh":"役所广司","ja":"役所広司","es":"Koji Yakusho"},{"en":"Ken Watanabe","zh":"渡边谦","ja":"渡辺謙","es":"Ken Watanabe"},{"en":"Toshiro Mifune","zh":"三船敏郎","ja":"三船敏郎","es":"Toshiro Mifune"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Ken Watanabe received an Academy Award nomination for Best Supporting Actor for his role in The Last Samurai (2003).","zh":"渡边谦因在《最后的武士》(2003)中的表演获得了奥斯卡最佳男配角提名。","ja":"渡辺謙は『ラストサムライ』(2003年)の演技でアカデミー助演男優賞にノミネートされました。","es":"Ken Watanabe recibió una nominación al Oscar como Mejor Actor de Reparto por su papel en El último samurái (2003)."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_019","q":{"en":"What is the Japanese term for TV variety shows?","zh":"日本电视综艺节目的日语说法是什么？","ja":"テレビのバラエティ番組を何と言いますか？","es":"¿Cuál es el término japonés para los programas de variedades de TV?"},"c":[{"en":"Dorama","zh":"电视剧","ja":"ドラマ","es":"Dorama"},{"en":"Anime","zh":"动画","ja":"アニメ","es":"Anime"},{"en":"Bangumi","zh":"节目","ja":"番組","es":"Bangumi"},{"en":"Baraetii","zh":"综艺","ja":"バラエティ","es":"Baraetii"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Japanese variety shows (baraetii) typically feature comedians, celebrities, food segments, and games in a single program.","zh":"日本综艺节目通常在一个节目中包含搞笑艺人、名人、美食环节和游戏。","ja":"日本のバラエティ番組は、お笑い芸人、タレント、グルメコーナー、ゲームなどが一つの番組に盛り込まれています。","es":"Los programas de variedades japoneses suelen incluir comediantes, celebridades, segmentos de comida y juegos en un solo programa."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_020","q":{"en":"What is the Japanese term for 'talent' or TV personality?","zh":"'艺人'或电视名人的日语说法是什么？","ja":"テレビで活躍する芸能人を何と呼びますか？","es":"¿Cuál es el término japonés para 'talento' o personalidad de TV?"},"c":[{"en":"Geinin","zh":"艺人","ja":"芸人","es":"Geinin"},{"en":"Tarento","zh":"达人","ja":"タレント","es":"Tarento"},{"en":"Aidoru","zh":"偶像","ja":"アイドル","es":"Aidoru"},{"en":"Sutaa","zh":"明星","ja":"スター","es":"Sutaa"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"The word 'tarento' comes from the English word 'talent' and refers to celebrities who appear on variety shows, commercials, and talk shows.","zh":"'タレント'一词来源于英语'talent'，指出现在综艺节目、广告和访谈节目中的名人。","ja":"『タレント』は英語の'talent'に由来し、バラエティ番組やCM、トーク番組に出演する芸能人を指します。","es":"La palabra 'tarento' proviene del inglés 'talent' y se refiere a celebridades que aparecen en programas de variedades, comerciales y programas de entrevistas."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_021","q":{"en":"Which NHK drama series features historical stories and airs on Sunday evenings?","zh":"NHK的哪个电视剧系列以历史故事为主题，在周日晚间播出？","ja":"NHKで日曜の夜に放送される歴史ドラマシリーズは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué serie de drama de NHK presenta historias históricas y se emite los domingos por la noche?"},"c":[{"en":"Asadora","zh":"晨间剧","ja":"朝ドラ","es":"Asadora"},{"en":"Nichiyou Gekijou","zh":"日曜剧场","ja":"日曜劇場","es":"Nichiyou Gekijou"},{"en":"Taiga Drama","zh":"大河剧","ja":"大河ドラマ","es":"Taiga Drama"},{"en":"Getsu-9","zh":"月九","ja":"月9","es":"Getsu-9"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Taiga Dramas have been broadcast since 1963, each running for a full year, covering important figures and events in Japanese history.","zh":"大河剧自1963年开始播出，每部播出一整年，讲述日本历史上的重要人物和事件。","ja":"大河ドラマは1963年から放送されており、各作品は1年間にわたって日本史の重要な人物や出来事を描きます。","es":"Los Taiga Dramas se transmiten desde 1963, cada uno durante un año completo, cubriendo figuras y eventos importantes de la historia japonesa."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_022","q":{"en":"What is 'owarai' in Japanese entertainment?","zh":"日本娱乐中的'お笑い'是什么？","ja":"日本の芸能における『お笑い』とは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué es 'owarai' en el entretenimiento japonés?"},"c":[{"en":"Action movies","zh":"动作电影","ja":"アクション映画","es":"Películas de acción"},{"en":"Horror dramas","zh":"恐怖剧","ja":"ホラードラマ","es":"Dramas de terror"},{"en":"Musical performances","zh":"音乐表演","ja":"音楽パフォーマンス","es":"Actuaciones musicales"},{"en":"Comedy and humor entertainment","zh":"喜剧和幽默娱乐","ja":"お笑い・コメディ","es":"Entretenimiento de comedia y humor"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Owarai (literally 'laughter') is a huge part of Japanese TV culture, with comedians being among the most popular TV personalities.","zh":"'お笑い'（字面意思为'笑'）是日本电视文化的重要组成部分，搞笑艺人是最受欢迎的电视名人之一。","ja":"お笑いは日本のテレビ文化の大きな部分を占めており、お笑い芸人はテレビで最も人気のあるタレントの一つです。","es":"Owarai (literalmente 'risa') es una parte enorme de la cultura televisiva japonesa, con los comediantes entre las personalidades de TV más populares."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_023","q":{"en":"Which Godzilla film was released in 2016 and directed by Hideaki Anno?","zh":"2016年上映、由庵野秀明导演的哥斯拉电影是哪部？","ja":"2016年公開の庵野秀明監督のゴジラ映画は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué película de Godzilla fue estrenada en 2016 y dirigida por Hideaki Anno?"},"c":[{"en":"Godzilla vs. Kong","zh":"哥斯拉大战金刚","ja":"ゴジラvsコング","es":"Godzilla vs. Kong"},{"en":"Shin Godzilla","zh":"新哥斯拉","ja":"シン・ゴジラ","es":"Shin Godzilla"},{"en":"Godzilla: Final Wars","zh":"哥斯拉：最终战争","ja":"ゴジラ ファイナルウォーズ","es":"Godzilla: Final Wars"},{"en":"Godzilla 2000","zh":"哥斯拉2000","ja":"ゴジラ2000","es":"Godzilla 2000"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Shin Godzilla was a critical and commercial hit in Japan, winning the Japan Academy Prize for Picture of the Year.","zh":"《新哥斯拉》在日本获得了评论和票房的双重成功，赢得了日本电影学院奖最佳影片奖。","ja":"『シン・ゴジラ』は日本で興行的にも批評的にも大成功を収め、日本アカデミー賞最優秀作品賞を受賞しました。","es":"Shin Godzilla fue un éxito de crítica y comercial en Japón, ganando el Premio de la Academia Japonesa a la Mejor Película del Año."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_024","q":{"en":"What is the Japanese word for TV drama series?","zh":"电视剧系列的日语说法是什么？","ja":"テレビドラマの日本語での言い方は何ですか？","es":"¿Cuál es la palabra japonesa para series de drama de TV?"},"c":[{"en":"Eiga","zh":"电影","ja":"映画","es":"Eiga"},{"en":"Shibai","zh":"戏剧","ja":"芝居","es":"Shibai"},{"en":"Dorama","zh":"电视剧","ja":"ドラマ","es":"Dorama"},{"en":"Gekijou","zh":"剧场","ja":"劇場","es":"Gekijou"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Japanese TV dramas (dorama) typically run for one season of 10-12 episodes, unlike American shows that may run for many seasons.","zh":"日本电视剧通常只播出一季10-12集，不像美剧可能播出多季。","ja":"日本のドラマは通常1クール10〜12話で完結するのが特徴で、複数シーズン続くアメリカのドラマとは異なります。","es":"Los dramas japoneses (dorama) suelen tener una temporada de 10-12 episodios, a diferencia de los programas americanos que pueden durar muchas temporadas."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_025","q":{"en":"Which Japanese comedian duo is known as 'Downtown'?","zh":"哪对日本搞笑组合被称为'Downtown'？","ja":"『ダウンタウン』として知られるお笑いコンビは誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué dúo de comediantes japoneses es conocido como 'Downtown'?"},"c":[{"en":"Sanma and Tamori","zh":"三明和塔莫利","ja":"さんまとタモリ","es":"Sanma y Tamori"},{"en":"Tanaka and Endo","zh":"田中和远藤","ja":"田中と遠藤","es":"Tanaka y Endo"},{"en":"Matsumoto and Hamada","zh":"松本和浜田","ja":"松本と浜田","es":"Matsumoto y Hamada"},{"en":"Atsushi and Ryo","zh":"敦和亮","ja":"敦と亮","es":"Atsushi y Ryo"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Downtown consists of Hitoshi Matsumoto and Masatoshi Hamada, and they are considered among the most influential comedians in Japanese TV history.","zh":"Downtown由松本人志和浜田雅功组成，被认为是日本电视史上最有影响力的搞笑艺人之一。","ja":"ダウンタウンは松本人志と浜田雅功のコンビで、日本のテレビ史上最も影響力のあるお笑い芸人の一組とされています。","es":"Downtown está formado por Hitoshi Matsumoto y Masatoshi Hamada, y son considerados entre los comediantes más influyentes de la historia de la TV japonesa."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_026","q":{"en":"What is the popular Japanese TV show where comedians must not laugh or face punishment?","zh":"日本有一档搞笑艺人不能笑否则受罚的人气节目叫什么？","ja":"お笑い芸人が笑ったら罰を受ける人気テレビ番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama el popular programa de TV japonés donde los comediantes no deben reírse o enfrentan un castigo?"},"c":[{"en":"Gaki no Tsukai (No Laughing)","zh":"绝对不能笑","ja":"ガキの使い（笑ってはいけない）","es":"Gaki no Tsukai (No reírse)"},{"en":"Takeshi's Castle","zh":"风云城堡","ja":"たけし城","es":"El castillo de Takeshi"},{"en":"Sasuke (Ninja Warrior)","zh":"极限体能王","ja":"SASUKE","es":"Sasuke (Ninja Warrior)"},{"en":"VS Arashi","zh":"VS岚","ja":"VS嵐","es":"VS Arashi"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"The 'No Laughing' batsu game specials by Downtown's Gaki no Tsukai air every New Year's Eve and have become a beloved tradition.","zh":"Downtown的《绝对不能笑》罚game特别节目每年除夕播出，已成为深受喜爱的传统。","ja":"ダウンタウンのガキの使いの『笑ってはいけない』シリーズは毎年大晦日に放送され、年末の風物詩となっています。","es":"Los especiales del juego de castigo 'No reírse' de Gaki no Tsukai de Downtown se emiten cada Nochevieja y se han convertido en una querida tradición."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_027","q":{"en":"Which Japanese film director made 'Departures', which won the Academy Award for Best Foreign Language Film in 2009?","zh":"哪位日本导演执导了2009年获得奥斯卡最佳外语片奖的《入殓师》？","ja":"2009年にアカデミー外国語映画賞を受賞した『おくりびと』の監督は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué director de cine japonés hizo 'Despedidas', que ganó el Oscar a la Mejor Película en Lengua Extranjera en 2009?"},"c":[{"en":"Hirokazu Kore-eda","zh":"是枝裕和","ja":"是枝裕和","es":"Hirokazu Kore-eda"},{"en":"Yojiro Takita","zh":"的场洋二郎","ja":"滝田洋二郎","es":"Yojiro Takita"},{"en":"Ryusuke Hamaguchi","zh":"滨口龙介","ja":"濱口竜介","es":"Ryusuke Hamaguchi"},{"en":"Takeshi Kitano","zh":"北野武","ja":"北野武","es":"Takeshi Kitano"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Departures (Okuribito) tells the story of a cellist who becomes a mortician and explores Japanese attitudes toward death.","zh":"《入殓师》讲述了一位大提琴手成为入殓师的故事，探讨了日本人对死亡的态度。","ja":"『おくりびと』はチェロ奏者が納棺師になる物語で、日本人の死に対する向き合い方を描いています。","es":"Despedidas (Okuribito) cuenta la historia de un chelista que se convierte en funerario y explora las actitudes japonesas hacia la muerte."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_028","q":{"en":"Which Japanese TV show features physical challenges and obstacle courses, known internationally as 'Ninja Warrior'?","zh":"哪档日本电视节目以体能挑战和障碍赛为特色，在国际上被称为'极限体能王'？","ja":"海外で'Ninja Warrior'として知られる体力チャレンジの日本のテレビ番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué programa de TV japonés presenta desafíos físicos y carreras de obstáculos, conocido internacionalmente como 'Ninja Warrior'?"},"c":[{"en":"Takeshi's Castle","zh":"风云城堡","ja":"たけし城","es":"El castillo de Takeshi"},{"en":"Kinniku Banzuke","zh":"肌肉擂台","ja":"筋肉番付","es":"Kinniku Banzuke"},{"en":"Sasuke","zh":"极限体能王","ja":"SASUKE","es":"Sasuke"},{"en":"Viking","zh":"维京","ja":"バイキング","es":"Viking"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"SASUKE first aired in 1997 on TBS and has inspired versions in over 10 countries, including American Ninja Warrior.","zh":"SASUKE于1997年在TBS首播，已在10多个国家推出翻版，包括美国的《美国忍者勇士》。","ja":"SASUKEは1997年にTBSで初放送され、アメリカの『American Ninja Warrior』など10カ国以上で各国版が制作されました。","es":"SASUKE se emitió por primera vez en 1997 en TBS y ha inspirado versiones en más de 10 países, incluyendo American Ninja Warrior."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_029","q":{"en":"Who are the 'Big Three' (BIG3) of Japanese comedy?","zh":"日本喜剧界的'BIG3'是谁？","ja":"日本のお笑いBIG3とは誰ですか？","es":"¿Quiénes son los 'Tres Grandes' (BIG3) de la comedia japonesa?"},"c":[{"en":"Matsumoto, Hamada, and Sanma","zh":"松本、浜田和三明","ja":"松本、浜田、さんま","es":"Matsumoto, Hamada y Sanma"},{"en":"Tamori, Takeshi, and Sanma","zh":"塔莫利、北野武和三明","ja":"タモリ、たけし、さんま","es":"Tamori, Takeshi y Sanma"},{"en":"Shimura, Kato, and Shinsuke","zh":"志村、加藤和伸介","ja":"志村、加藤、紳助","es":"Shimura, Kato y Shinsuke"},{"en":"Tunnels and Sanma","zh":"隧道和三明","ja":"とんねるずとさんま","es":"Tunnels y Sanma"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Tamori, Beat Takeshi, and Akashiya Sanma have dominated Japanese variety TV since the 1980s and are considered entertainment legends.","zh":"塔莫利、北野武和明石家三明自1980年代以来主宰日本综艺电视，被视为娱乐界的传奇。","ja":"タモリ、ビートたけし、明石家さんまは1980年代から日本のバラエティ番組を席巻し、芸能界のレジェンドとされています。","es":"Tamori, Beat Takeshi y Akashiya Sanma han dominado la TV de variedades japonesa desde la década de 1980 y son considerados leyendas del entretenimiento."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_030","q":{"en":"Which Studio Ghibli film tells the story of a young witch starting a delivery service?","zh":"哪部吉卜力电影讲述了一个小魔女开快递服务的故事？","ja":"若い魔女が宅急便を始める物語のスタジオジブリ映画は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué película de Studio Ghibli cuenta la historia de una joven bruja que inicia un servicio de entregas?"},"c":[{"en":"The Secret World of Arrietty","zh":"借东西的小人阿莉埃蒂","ja":"借りぐらしのアリエッティ","es":"El mundo secreto de Arrietty"},{"en":"Spirited Away","zh":"千与千寻","ja":"千と千尋の神隠し","es":"El viaje de Chihiro"},{"en":"Howl's Moving Castle","zh":"哈尔的移动城堡","ja":"ハウルの動く城","es":"El castillo ambulante"},{"en":"Kiki's Delivery Service","zh":"魔女宅急便","ja":"魔女の宅急便","es":"Kiki: Entregas a domicilio"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Kiki's Delivery Service (1989) was inspired by a novel by Eiko Kadono and became a beloved classic about independence and growing up.","zh":"《魔女宅急便》(1989)改编自角野荣子的小说，成为关于独立和成长的经典之作。","ja":"『魔女の宅急便』(1989年)は角野栄子の小説を原作とし、自立と成長を描いた名作です。","es":"Kiki: Entregas a domicilio (1989) se inspiró en una novela de Eiko Kadono y se convirtió en un clásico querido sobre la independencia y el crecimiento."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_031","q":{"en":"What is the name of the famous Japanese game show hosted by Takeshi Kitano in the 1980s?","zh":"1980年代由北野武主持的著名日本游戏节目叫什么？","ja":"1980年代にビートたけしが出演した有名なゲーム番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Cómo se llama el famoso programa de juegos japonés presentado por Takeshi Kitano en los años 80?"},"c":[{"en":"Sasuke","zh":"极限体能王","ja":"SASUKE","es":"Sasuke"},{"en":"Takeshi's Castle","zh":"风云城堡","ja":"風雲！たけし城","es":"El castillo de Takeshi"},{"en":"Gaki no Tsukai","zh":"整人大赏","ja":"ガキの使い","es":"Gaki no Tsukai"},{"en":"Iron Chef","zh":"铁人料理","ja":"料理の鉄人","es":"Iron Chef"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Takeshi's Castle featured contestants attempting to storm a castle through various wacky physical challenges and has been adapted worldwide.","zh":"《风云城堡》中参赛者通过各种搞怪的体能挑战试图攻占城堡，该节目已被全球多国翻拍。","ja":"『風雲！たけし城』は参加者がさまざまなユニークな体力チャレンジでたけし城を攻略する番組で、世界中でリメイクされています。","es":"El castillo de Takeshi presentaba a concursantes intentando asaltar un castillo a través de varios desafíos físicos alocados y ha sido adaptado en todo el mundo."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_032","q":{"en":"Which Japanese cooking competition TV show featured 'Iron Chefs'?","zh":"哪档日本烹饪比赛电视节目以'铁人厨师'为特色？","ja":"『鉄人シェフ』が登場する日本の料理対決番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué programa de TV de competición de cocina japonesa presentaba a los 'Iron Chefs'?"},"c":[{"en":"Cooking Papa","zh":"妙厨老爸","ja":"クッキングパパ","es":"Cooking Papa"},{"en":"Iron Chef (Ryori no Tetsujin)","zh":"铁人料理","ja":"料理の鉄人","es":"Iron Chef (Ryori no Tetsujin)"},{"en":"Kitchen Battle","zh":"厨房大战","ja":"キッチンバトル","es":"Kitchen Battle"},{"en":"Master Chef Japan","zh":"日本大厨","ja":"マスターシェフジャパン","es":"Master Chef Japan"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Iron Chef ran from 1993 to 1999 on Fuji TV and was so popular that it spawned the American version 'Iron Chef America'.","zh":"《铁人料理》从1993年到1999年在富士电视台播出，因大受欢迎而催生了美国版《美国铁人料理》。","ja":"『料理の鉄人』は1993年から1999年までフジテレビで放送され、大人気となり、アメリカ版『Iron Chef America』も制作されました。","es":"Iron Chef se emitió de 1993 a 1999 en Fuji TV y fue tan popular que generó la versión americana 'Iron Chef America'."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_033","q":{"en":"What is the Tokyo International Film Festival?","zh":"东京国际电影节是什么？","ja":"東京国際映画祭とは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué es el Festival Internacional de Cine de Tokio?"},"c":[{"en":"A music festival in Tokyo","zh":"东京的音乐节","ja":"東京の音楽祭","es":"Un festival de música en Tokio"},{"en":"A TV drama awards ceremony","zh":"电视剧颁奖典礼","ja":"テレビドラマの授賞式","es":"Una ceremonia de premios de drama de TV"},{"en":"Japan's largest international film festival","zh":"日本最大的国际电影节","ja":"日本最大の国際映画祭","es":"El festival internacional de cine más grande de Japón"},{"en":"An anime convention","zh":"动漫展","ja":"アニメコンベンション","es":"Una convención de anime"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"The Tokyo International Film Festival (TIFF) has been held annually since 1985 and is one of Asia's major film festivals.","zh":"东京国际电影节自1985年起每年举办，是亚洲主要电影节之一。","ja":"東京国際映画祭（TIFF）は1985年から毎年開催されており、アジアを代表する映画祭の一つです。","es":"El Festival Internacional de Cine de Tokio (TIFF) se celebra anualmente desde 1985 y es uno de los principales festivales de cine de Asia."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_034","q":{"en":"Which famous Japanese TV host hosted 'Waratte Iitomo!' for over 30 years?","zh":"哪位著名日本电视主持人主持了《笑着好吗》超过30年？","ja":"『笑っていいとも！』を30年以上司会した有名なテレビタレントは誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué famoso presentador de TV japonés presentó 'Waratte Iitomo!' durante más de 30 años?"},"c":[{"en":"Beat Takeshi","zh":"北野武","ja":"ビートたけし","es":"Beat Takeshi"},{"en":"Akashiya Sanma","zh":"明石家三明","ja":"明石家さんま","es":"Akashiya Sanma"},{"en":"Shimura Ken","zh":"志村健","ja":"志村けん","es":"Shimura Ken"},{"en":"Tamori","zh":"塔莫利","ja":"タモリ","es":"Tamori"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Tamori hosted Waratte Iitomo! from 1982 to 2014, making it one of the longest-running live TV shows in the world.","zh":"塔莫利从1982年到2014年主持《笑着好吗》，使其成为世界上播出时间最长的直播电视节目之一。","ja":"タモリは1982年から2014年まで『笑っていいとも！』を司会し、世界でも最も長く続いた生放送のテレビ番組の一つとなりました。","es":"Tamori presentó Waratte Iitomo! de 1982 a 2014, convirtiéndolo en uno de los programas de TV en vivo más longevos del mundo."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_035","q":{"en":"What is the Studio Ghibli film 'Princess Mononoke' about?","zh":"吉卜力电影《幽灵公主》讲的是什么？","ja":"スタジオジブリの映画『もののけ姫』はどんな内容ですか？","es":"¿De qué trata la película de Studio Ghibli 'La princesa Mononoke'?"},"c":[{"en":"A girl working in a bathhouse","zh":"一个在澡堂工作的女孩","ja":"銭湯で働く少女","es":"Una chica trabajando en una casa de baños"},{"en":"A conflict between humans and forest spirits","zh":"人类和森林精灵之间的冲突","ja":"人間と森の精霊たちの対立","es":"Un conflicto entre humanos y espíritus del bosque"},{"en":"A flying castle adventure","zh":"飞行城堡冒险","ja":"空飛ぶ城の冒険","es":"Una aventura en un castillo volador"},{"en":"A witch delivering packages","zh":"魔女送快递","ja":"魔女の宅配","es":"Una bruja entregando paquetes"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Princess Mononoke (1997) was the highest-grossing Japanese film until Spirited Away surpassed it in 2001.","zh":"《幽灵公主》(1997)曾是日本票房最高的电影，直到2001年被《千与千寻》超越。","ja":"『もののけ姫』(1997年)は日本映画の歴代興行収入1位でしたが、2001年に『千と千尋の神隠し』に抜かれました。","es":"La princesa Mononoke (1997) fue la película japonesa más taquillera hasta que El viaje de Chihiro la superó en 2001."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_036","q":{"en":"What does the Japanese word 'eiga' mean?","zh":"日语中的'映画'是什么意思？","ja":"日本語の『映画』はどういう意味ですか？","es":"¿Qué significa la palabra japonesa 'eiga'?"},"c":[{"en":"Television","zh":"电视","ja":"テレビ","es":"Televisión"},{"en":"Music","zh":"音乐","ja":"音楽","es":"Música"},{"en":"Movie/Film","zh":"电影","ja":"映画","es":"Película/Film"},{"en":"Theater","zh":"剧场","ja":"劇場","es":"Teatro"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"The word 'eiga' literally means 'reflected pictures' and has been used to describe movies since cinema was introduced to Japan in the late 1800s.","zh":"'映画'字面意思为'映射的画'，自19世纪末电影传入日本以来一直用来描述电影。","ja":"『映画』は文字通り『映し出された画』という意味で、1800年代後半に映画が日本に伝わって以来使われています。","es":"La palabra 'eiga' significa literalmente 'imágenes reflejadas' y se ha usado para describir películas desde que el cine fue introducido en Japón a finales de 1800."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_037","q":{"en":"Which Japanese horror film from 1998 features a cursed videotape?","zh":"1998年的哪部日本恐怖电影以一盘被诅咒的录像带为主题？","ja":"1998年の呪いのビデオテープが登場する日本のホラー映画は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué película de terror japonesa de 1998 presenta una cinta de video maldita?"},"c":[{"en":"Ju-On (The Grudge)","zh":"咒怨","ja":"呪怨","es":"Ju-On (La maldición)"},{"en":"Dark Water","zh":"鬼水怪谈","ja":"仄暗い水の底から","es":"Dark Water"},{"en":"Audition","zh":"切肤之爱","ja":"オーディション","es":"Audition"},{"en":"Ring (Ringu)","zh":"午夜凶铃","ja":"リング","es":"Ring (Ringu)"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Ring (Ringu) helped launch the J-horror boom worldwide and was remade in Hollywood as 'The Ring' in 2002.","zh":"《午夜凶铃》在全球掀起了日本恐怖片热潮，2002年被好莱坞翻拍为《午夜凶铃》美国版。","ja":"『リング』は世界的なJホラーブームの火付け役となり、2002年にハリウッドで『ザ・リング』としてリメイクされました。","es":"Ring (Ringu) ayudó a lanzar el boom del J-horror en todo el mundo y fue rehecha en Hollywood como 'The Ring' en 2002."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_038","q":{"en":"What are Japanese idols (aidoru)?","zh":"日本的偶像（アイドル）是什么？","ja":"日本の『アイドル』とは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué son los ídolos japoneses (aidoru)?"},"c":[{"en":"Religious statues","zh":"宗教雕像","ja":"宗教的な像","es":"Estatuas religiosas"},{"en":"Traditional puppet performers","zh":"传统木偶表演者","ja":"伝統的な人形遣い","es":"Artistas de marionetas tradicionales"},{"en":"Young pop entertainers marketed for their image and personality","zh":"以形象和个性进行营销的年轻流行艺人","ja":"イメージとキャラクターで売り出される若いポップエンターテイナー","es":"Jóvenes artistas pop comercializados por su imagen y personalidad"},{"en":"Sumo wrestlers","zh":"相扑选手","ja":"力士","es":"Luchadores de sumo"}],"a":2,"trivia":{"en":"Japanese idol culture began in the 1970s and has grown into a massive industry including groups like AKB48 and Morning Musume.","zh":"日本偶像文化始于1970年代，已发展成包括AKB48和早安少女组等在内的庞大产业。","ja":"日本のアイドル文化は1970年代に始まり、AKB48やモーニング娘。などを含む巨大な産業に成長しました。","es":"La cultura idol japonesa comenzó en la década de 1970 y ha crecido hasta convertirse en una industria masiva que incluye grupos como AKB48 y Morning Musume."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_039","q":{"en":"Which long-running Japanese comedy show featured Shimura Ken and was beloved by all ages?","zh":"哪档长寿日本喜剧节目由志村健主持，深受各年龄段观众喜爱？","ja":"志村けんが出演し、老若男女に愛された長寿お笑い番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué programa de comedia japonés de larga duración presentó a Shimura Ken y fue amado por todas las edades?"},"c":[{"en":"Shimura Ken no Bakatonosama","zh":"志村健的傻殿下","ja":"志村けんのバカ殿様","es":"Shimura Ken no Bakatonosama"},{"en":"Lincoln","zh":"Lincoln","ja":"リンカーン","es":"Lincoln"},{"en":"Ametalk","zh":"雨上决死队的脱口秀","ja":"アメトーーク","es":"Ametalk"},{"en":"Shabekuri 007","zh":"唠叨007","ja":"しゃべくり007","es":"Shabekuri 007"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"Shimura Ken (1950-2020) was one of Japan's most beloved comedians, known for his slapstick humor and family-friendly comedy.","zh":"志村健（1950-2020）是日本最受喜爱的喜剧演员之一，以闹剧幽默和合家欢喜剧闻名。","ja":"志村けん（1950-2020）は日本で最も愛されたお笑い芸人の一人で、コントやファミリー向けの笑いで知られました。","es":"Shimura Ken (1950-2020) fue uno de los comediantes más queridos de Japón, conocido por su humor físico y comedia familiar."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_040","q":{"en":"Which Hayao Miyazaki film features a castle that walks on mechanical legs?","zh":"宫崎骏的哪部电影中有一座用机械腿行走的城堡？","ja":"機械の足で歩く城が登場する宮崎駿の映画は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué película de Hayao Miyazaki presenta un castillo que camina con patas mecánicas?"},"c":[{"en":"Castle in the Sky","zh":"天空之城","ja":"天空の城ラピュタ","es":"El castillo en el cielo"},{"en":"Nausicaa of the Valley of the Wind","zh":"风之谷","ja":"風の谷のナウシカ","es":"Nausicaä del Valle del Viento"},{"en":"The Wind Rises","zh":"起风了","ja":"風立ちぬ","es":"El viento se levanta"},{"en":"Howl's Moving Castle","zh":"哈尔的移动城堡","ja":"ハウルの動く城","es":"El castillo ambulante"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Howl's Moving Castle (2004) is based on a novel by British author Diana Wynne Jones and was nominated for an Academy Award.","zh":"《哈尔的移动城堡》(2004)改编自英国作家戴安娜·韦恩·琼斯的小说，获得了奥斯卡提名。","ja":"『ハウルの動く城』(2004年)はイギリスの作家ダイアナ・ウィン・ジョーンズの小説が原作で、アカデミー賞にノミネートされました。","es":"El castillo ambulante (2004) está basado en una novela de la autora británica Diana Wynne Jones y fue nominada al Oscar."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_041","q":{"en":"What is 'jidaigeki' in Japanese entertainment?","zh":"日本娱乐中的'时代剧'是什么？","ja":"日本の芸能における『時代劇』とは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué es 'jidaigeki' en el entretenimiento japonés?"},"c":[{"en":"Science fiction shows","zh":"科幻节目","ja":"SF番組","es":"Programas de ciencia ficción"},{"en":"Historical period dramas","zh":"历史时代剧","ja":"歴史時代劇","es":"Dramas de época histórica"},{"en":"Modern romance dramas","zh":"现代爱情剧","ja":"現代恋愛ドラマ","es":"Dramas románticos modernos"},{"en":"Game shows","zh":"游戏节目","ja":"ゲーム番組","es":"Programas de juegos"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Jidaigeki typically depict the Edo period (1603-1868) and feature samurai, sword fights, and stories of honor and duty.","zh":"时代剧通常描绘江户时代（1603-1868），以武士、剑斗、荣誉和责任为主题。","ja":"時代劇は主に江戸時代（1603〜1868年）を舞台に、侍や剣戟、義理と人情の物語を描きます。","es":"Los jidaigeki típicamente representan el período Edo (1603-1868) y presentan samuráis, luchas con espadas e historias de honor y deber."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_042","q":{"en":"Which Japanese film won the Palme d'Or at the Cannes Film Festival in 2018?","zh":"哪部日本电影在2018年戛纳电影节上获得了金棕榈奖？","ja":"2018年のカンヌ映画祭でパルムドールを受賞した日本映画は何ですか？","es":"¿Qué película japonesa ganó la Palma de Oro en el Festival de Cine de Cannes en 2018?"},"c":[{"en":"Shoplifters","zh":"小偷家族","ja":"万引き家族","es":"Un asunto de familia"},{"en":"Drive My Car","zh":"驾驶我的车","ja":"ドライブ・マイ・カー","es":"Drive My Car"},{"en":"Departures","zh":"入殓师","ja":"おくりびと","es":"Despedidas"},{"en":"Your Name","zh":"你的名字","ja":"君の名は。","es":"Your Name"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"Shoplifters was directed by Hirokazu Kore-eda and tells the story of a poor family that survives through petty theft.","zh":"《小偷家族》由是枝裕和导演，讲述了一个靠小偷小摸生存的贫困家庭的故事。","ja":"『万引き家族』は是枝裕和監督作品で、万引きで生計を立てる貧しい家族の物語です。","es":"Un asunto de familia fue dirigida por Hirokazu Kore-eda y cuenta la historia de una familia pobre que sobrevive mediante pequeños robos."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_043","q":{"en":"What is 'Music Station' in Japan?","zh":"日本的'Music Station'是什么？","ja":"日本の『ミュージックステーション』とは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué es 'Music Station' en Japón?"},"c":[{"en":"A radio station","zh":"广播电台","ja":"ラジオ局","es":"Una estación de radio"},{"en":"A concert hall","zh":"音乐厅","ja":"コンサートホール","es":"Una sala de conciertos"},{"en":"A music streaming service","zh":"音乐流媒体服务","ja":"音楽ストリーミングサービス","es":"Un servicio de streaming de música"},{"en":"A weekly live music TV show","zh":"每周直播音乐电视节目","ja":"毎週放送の音楽番組","es":"Un programa de TV de música en vivo semanal"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Music Station (M-Sta) has aired on TV Asahi since 1986 and is Japan's most famous weekly music program.","zh":"Music Station自1986年在朝日电视台播出，是日本最著名的每周音乐节目。","ja":"ミュージックステーション（Mステ）は1986年からテレビ朝日で放送されている日本で最も有名な週刊音楽番組です。","es":"Music Station (M-Sta) se emite en TV Asahi desde 1986 y es el programa musical semanal más famoso de Japón."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_044","q":{"en":"Which famous Japanese actor was known for starring in many of Akira Kurosawa's films?","zh":"哪位著名日本演员以出演黑泽明的多部电影闻名？","ja":"黒澤明監督の多くの映画に出演したことで知られる有名な日本の俳優は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué famoso actor japonés fue conocido por protagonizar muchas películas de Akira Kurosawa?"},"c":[{"en":"Ken Watanabe","zh":"渡边谦","ja":"渡辺謙","es":"Ken Watanabe"},{"en":"Toshiro Mifune","zh":"三船敏郎","ja":"三船敏郎","es":"Toshiro Mifune"},{"en":"Tatsuya Nakadai","zh":"仲代达矢","ja":"仲代達矢","es":"Tatsuya Nakadai"},{"en":"Takashi Shimura","zh":"志村乔","ja":"志村喬","es":"Takashi Shimura"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Toshiro Mifune appeared in 16 of Kurosawa's films and is considered one of the greatest actors in Japanese cinema history.","zh":"三船敏郎出演了黑泽明的16部电影，被认为是日本电影史上最伟大的演员之一。","ja":"三船敏郎は黒澤明の16作品に出演し、日本映画史上最も偉大な俳優の一人とされています。","es":"Toshiro Mifune apareció en 16 películas de Kurosawa y es considerado uno de los más grandes actores de la historia del cine japonés."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_045","q":{"en":"What is the popular Japanese reality TV dating show that streams on Netflix?","zh":"在Netflix上播出的日本人气真人秀约会节目是什么？","ja":"Netflixで配信されている人気の日本の恋愛リアリティ番組は何ですか？","es":"¿Cuál es el popular programa de citas de reality TV japonés que se transmite en Netflix?"},"c":[{"en":"The Bachelor Japan","zh":"日本单身汉","ja":"バチェラー・ジャパン","es":"The Bachelor Japan"},{"en":"Terrace House","zh":"双层公寓","ja":"テラスハウス","es":"Terrace House"},{"en":"Love Island Japan","zh":"爱情岛日本","ja":"ラブアイランドジャパン","es":"Love Island Japan"},{"en":"Heart Signal Japan","zh":"心动信号日本","ja":"ハートシグナルジャパン","es":"Heart Signal Japan"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Terrace House featured six strangers living together with no scripts, and became an international hit on Netflix, known for its calm and polite tone.","zh":"《双层公寓》中六个陌生人无剧本同住，在Netflix上成为国际热门节目，以平和礼貌的风格闻名。","ja":"テラスハウスは6人の男女が台本なしで共同生活する番組で、Netflixで国際的なヒットとなり、穏やかで礼儀正しい雰囲気で知られています。","es":"Terrace House presentaba a seis desconocidos viviendo juntos sin guion, y se convirtió en un éxito internacional en Netflix, conocido por su tono calmado y educado."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_046","q":{"en":"Which Japanese director made 'Drive My Car', which won the Academy Award for Best International Feature Film in 2022?","zh":"哪位日本导演执导了2022年获得奥斯卡最佳国际影片奖的《驾驶我的车》？","ja":"2022年にアカデミー国際長編映画賞を受賞した『ドライブ・マイ・カー』の監督は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué director japonés hizo 'Drive My Car', que ganó el Oscar a la Mejor Película Internacional en 2022?"},"c":[{"en":"Hirokazu Kore-eda","zh":"是枝裕和","ja":"是枝裕和","es":"Hirokazu Kore-eda"},{"en":"Makoto Shinkai","zh":"新海诚","ja":"新海誠","es":"Makoto Shinkai"},{"en":"Hayao Miyazaki","zh":"宫崎骏","ja":"宮崎駿","es":"Hayao Miyazaki"},{"en":"Ryusuke Hamaguchi","zh":"滨口龙介","ja":"濱口竜介","es":"Ryusuke Hamaguchi"}],"a":3,"trivia":{"en":"Drive My Car is based on a short story by Haruki Murakami and also won Best Screenplay at the Cannes Film Festival.","zh":"《驾驶我的车》改编自村上春树的短篇小说，还在戛纳电影节上获得了最佳编剧奖。","ja":"『ドライブ・マイ・カー』は村上春樹の短編小説が原作で、カンヌ映画祭では脚本賞も受賞しました。","es":"Drive My Car está basada en un cuento de Haruki Murakami y también ganó el Mejor Guion en el Festival de Cine de Cannes."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_047","q":{"en":"What does the Japanese word 'bangumi' mean?","zh":"日语中的'番组'是什么意思？","ja":"日本語の『番組』はどういう意味ですか？","es":"¿Qué significa la palabra japonesa 'bangumi'?"},"c":[{"en":"Commercial","zh":"广告","ja":"コマーシャル","es":"Comercial"},{"en":"TV program/show","zh":"电视节目","ja":"テレビ番組","es":"Programa/show de TV"},{"en":"News report","zh":"新闻报道","ja":"ニュース報道","es":"Informe de noticias"},{"en":"Movie theater","zh":"电影院","ja":"映画館","es":"Cine"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"The word 'bangumi' is used for all types of TV programs in Japan, from dramas and variety shows to news and documentaries.","zh":"'番组'一词用于日本所有类型的电视节目，从电视剧、综艺节目到新闻和纪录片。","ja":"『番組』はドラマ、バラエティ、ニュース、ドキュメンタリーなど、あらゆるテレビ番組を指す言葉です。","es":"La palabra 'bangumi' se usa para todo tipo de programas de TV en Japón, desde dramas y programas de variedades hasta noticias y documentales."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_048","q":{"en":"Which Japanese drama genre features stories about workplace struggles and office life?","zh":"哪种日剧类型以职场奋斗和办公室生活为主题？","ja":"職場での奮闘やオフィスライフを描く日本のドラマジャンルは何ですか？","es":"¿Qué género de drama japonés presenta historias sobre luchas laborales y vida de oficina?"},"c":[{"en":"Oshigoto dorama","zh":"职场剧","ja":"お仕事ドラマ","es":"Oshigoto dorama"},{"en":"Ren'ai dorama","zh":"恋爱剧","ja":"恋愛ドラマ","es":"Ren'ai dorama"},{"en":"Jidaigeki","zh":"时代剧","ja":"時代劇","es":"Jidaigeki"},{"en":"Gakuen dorama","zh":"校园剧","ja":"学園ドラマ","es":"Gakuen dorama"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"Workplace dramas are extremely popular in Japan and cover professions from doctors and lawyers to chefs and detectives.","zh":"职场剧在日本非常受欢迎，涵盖从医生、律师到厨师、侦探等各种职业。","ja":"お仕事ドラマは日本で非常に人気があり、医師、弁護士、シェフ、刑事など様々な職業を扱います。","es":"Los dramas laborales son extremadamente populares en Japón y cubren profesiones desde médicos y abogados hasta chefs y detectives."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_049","q":{"en":"What is Japan's oldest and most prestigious film magazine?","zh":"日本历史最悠久、最有声望的电影杂志是什么？","ja":"日本で最も歴史があり権威ある映画雑誌は何ですか？","es":"¿Cuál es la revista de cine más antigua y prestigiosa de Japón?"},"c":[{"en":"Kinema Junpo","zh":"电影旬报","ja":"キネマ旬報","es":"Kinema Junpo"},{"en":"Animage","zh":"Animage","ja":"アニメージュ","es":"Animage"},{"en":"Pia","zh":"Pia","ja":"ぴあ","es":"Pia"},{"en":"Eiga Hiho","zh":"电影秘宝","ja":"映画秘宝","es":"Eiga Hiho"}],"a":0,"trivia":{"en":"Kinema Junpo has been published since 1919 and its annual Best Ten list is the oldest film award in Japan.","zh":"《电影旬报》自1919年创刊，其年度十佳榜单是日本最古老的电影奖项。","ja":"キネマ旬報は1919年に創刊され、毎年のベスト・テンは日本最古の映画賞です。","es":"Kinema Junpo se publica desde 1919 y su lista anual de las Diez Mejores es el premio cinematográfico más antiguo de Japón."}},

{"id":"entertainment_beginner_050","q":{"en":"Which Japanese actress starred in 'Kill Bill' as Gogo Yubari?","zh":"哪位日本女演员在《杀死比尔》中饰演Gogo Yubari？","ja":"『キル・ビル』でゴーゴー夕張を演じた日本の女優は誰ですか？","es":"¿Qué actriz japonesa protagonizó 'Kill Bill' como Gogo Yubari?"},"c":[{"en":"Rinko Kikuchi","zh":"菊地凛子","ja":"菊地凛子","es":"Rinko Kikuchi"},{"en":"Chiaki Kuriyama","zh":"栗山千明","ja":"栗山千明","es":"Chiaki Kuriyama"},{"en":"Meiko Kaji","zh":"梶芽衣子","ja":"梶芽衣子","es":"Meiko Kaji"},{"en":"Ko Shibasaki","zh":"柴崎幸","ja":"柴咲コウ","es":"Ko Shibasaki"}],"a":1,"trivia":{"en":"Chiaki Kuriyama had previously starred in the Japanese film Battle Royale before being cast in Kill Bill by Quentin Tarantino.","zh":"栗山千明在被昆汀·塔伦蒂诺选入《杀死比尔》之前，曾出演日本电影《大逃杀》。","ja":"栗山千明はクエンティン・タランティーノに『キル・ビル』に抜擢される前、日本映画『バトル・ロワイアル』に出演していました。","es":"Chiaki Kuriyama había protagonizado previamente la película japonesa Battle Royale antes de ser seleccionada para Kill Bill por Quentin Tarantino."}},
